---
// src/pages/reviews/apple-sydney-opera-house.astro
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Apple Sydney Opera House Collaboration 2026">
  <article class="review">
    <header class="review-header">
      <span class="category">News</span>
      <h1>Apple Partners with Sydney Opera House for Yearlong Creativity Initiative</h1>
      <div class="meta">
        <span>By ReviewCloud</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>March 6, 2026</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="toc">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>Apple and the Sydney Opera House have announced a yearlong collaboration to inspire the next generation of creatives in Australia.</p>
    </div>

    <section>
      <h2>What to Expect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Founding Partner</strong> of new international children's festival</li>
        <li><strong>Procreate Artwork</strong> - 10 Australian artists will create artwork on iPad</li>
        <li><strong>Illumination Event</strong> - March 25-27, Opera House sails will display artwork</li>
        <li><strong>Free Today at Apple</strong> sessions for public participation</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Quote from Apple</h2>
      <blockquote>
        "For 50 years, Apple has been at the forefront of empowering creativity, providing tools that allow people to imagine, design, and share their unique visions with the world."
        <footer>— Greg Joswiak, Apple's marketing chief</footer>
      </blockquote>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Get Involved</h2>
      <p>From March 25 to March 27, visit the Sydney Opera House to see the illuminated artwork created in Procreate on iPad. Free Today at Apple sessions will allow the public to create and submit their own artwork for potential display.</p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .review { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; background: white; }
  .review-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .category { background: #667eea; color: white; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.875rem; }
  .review-header h1 { font-size: 1.75rem; margin: 1rem 0; }
  .meta { color: #666; display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; justify-content: center; }
  .toc { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #333; }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin: 0.5rem 0; color: #555; }
  blockquote { border-left: 4px solid #667eea; padding-left: 1rem; font-style: italic; color: #555; margin: 1rem 0; }
  blockquote footer { font-size: 0.875rem; color: #666; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
</style>
